Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:20.77,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.07,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:29.89,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between\Nthe sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good\Ntime just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.34,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.28,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.23,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:41.99,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing,\Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave\Nthe rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.53,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:02:00.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.87,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.62,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.47,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.64,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:15.71,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.91,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.65,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.00,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.54,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:39.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.67,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, \Na boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become\N the next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and\N less able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was ejected from \Nthe Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by Bartholomew Kuma, a Warlord of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from his friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he arrived alone at the female-only \Nempire of Amazon Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captured by the Pirate Empress Hancock,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy battled in mortal combat \Nwith her younger sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sandersonia and Marigold who had \Neaten the Snake-Snake Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mari! Get him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, Sister Sonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are now... being protected...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you'd rather die\N than show it to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hancock's Confession \NThe Sister's Abhorrent Past"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Sonia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry that we lost and \Nhad to be saved by our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you up next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that she's not damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these people you turned to stone; \Nturn them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were just trying to defend me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can revert them if I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you want \Nto go someplace by ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my crew's waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can only make \None of your wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's either revert them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or help you to get off this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose one wish and give up on the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snake Princess. You are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reveal your true nature, Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're going to help them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... very much!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't hesitate at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it that a man who has such great Haki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bows his head in order \Nto save his benefactors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he defeated the sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Snake Princess will forgive him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he was so rude to her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor will she forgive the people \Nwho let him in to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margaret!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweetpea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aphelandra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here you all are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! She turned you back from stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried because you \Nsuddenly started to vouch for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of what would happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turned us back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have absolutely no recollection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next thing I knew, that man\N was there and he was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried that you were going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all finished now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snake Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep dedicating yourself to \Nyour duty to protect our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...And that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're turned to stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard to remember what \Nhappened before and after.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Snake Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she turn him to stone this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems like he got\N summoned to the Kuja Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to know! \NWhat do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a meal after the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what it is, I'll be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of food is popular here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's some kind of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you" isn't something I can eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anybody had seen what's on our backs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no way that we \Ncould stay in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come inside, Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside of the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that where the food is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're not eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing \Nwith your clothes off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, you are reacting rudely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you had seen somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at it, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the meaning of this mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something I want to show people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, it's a bit different \Nfrom what I've seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a friend called Hachi \Nwho is a fish-man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fish-man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he has a similar mark on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought it was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about your mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't know, why don't you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Nyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come in from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest, Snake Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have seen clearly\N how tolerant that man is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him everything that you want to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a pirate,\N Monkey D. Luffy, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so casual
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after you caused such\N a sensation in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this newspaper! \NJust days ago, this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at Sabaody Archipelago \Nnear the center sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,caused a horrific and grave incident
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he dealt a blow to a Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dealt a blow to a Celestial Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a miracle that he was able to get away
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the supreme powers\N at the center sea after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in only a couple days,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he arrived here so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all beyond our understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was blown away suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea where this place is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and another thing -
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel sorry for that Celestial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what he did to my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is true that you punched \Na Celestial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...foolish people like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who put their lives at risk \Nto challenge those celestials...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you everything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including the meaning of the symbol
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that your fish-man friend \Nhas on his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi's mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Claw of the Celestial Dragon."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emblem of the Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who were fed by \Nthe World Nobles all get...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this permanent brand to \Nshow that you are subhuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us were...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...once...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...slaves of World Nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were... slaves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened when I was 12...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starboard, all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Port, all clear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow, all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High visibility, all serene!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're hungry! I brought a snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonia! Mari! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of us were taken \Nfrom the Kuja pirate ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we were sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all we have are terrible memories \Nthat we don't even want to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw men for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they were nothing but figures of horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Sonia, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The memory haunts us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow! H-Hey! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to force the memories! \NYou don't have to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We kept thinking about death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one night four years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something happened that made \Nthe World Government tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nobody will challenge \Nthe Celestial Dragons."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the cardinal rule in their world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was a man who climbed \Nthe Red Line with his bare hands
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and slipped into the Celestial \NDragons' Holyland of Marejois.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was an adventurer who\N later led the Fish-Man Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,named Fisher Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to free all the slaves
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the town there his fellow\N fish-men were being tortured,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he fought with all his might.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are free! We are free!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disliked humans as a species
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was being fair to all slaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let thousands of slaves \Nof different species go free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We prepared to die and ran among the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe him an immeasurable debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger released many fish-men to the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but ones who were slaves had \Na mark that cannot be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger has made the World Government his enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he formed the \NSun Pirates with former slaves
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sailed out into the open sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As though breaking a curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he changed the Celestial Dragon's \Nemblem on everyone's bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...into the symbol of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you thought was similar \Nto the mark on my back is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sun symbol of the Sun Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one Hachi has on his \Nforehead looks like the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he was a slave, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't necessarily mean that he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mark is made in such a way \Nthat it is impossible to tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...whether they are former slaves or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that he once was \Na member of the Sun Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, Fisher Tiger is already dead and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:20:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Sun Pirates have split \Nup into several groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when did you get hurt there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a complicated past, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the reason \Nthat the mark on our backs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is similar to the fish-men's mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I pretty much understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly, when we were slaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were forced to eat Love-Love Fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Snake-Snake Fruit\N for their entertainment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that enabled us to deceive our nation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and preserve the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't cover up \NSonia's back at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been impossible \Nfor us to stay on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to let anyone \Nknow about our past!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop at deceiving \Nour whole nation to hide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't open ourselves up at any price!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want anybody to \Ntake advantage of us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of being caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It terrifies me. I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the first time in a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you've shown your emotions like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I've thought \Nthat the Snake Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must have turned to ice or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a traitor who \Nleft the country behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three were miserable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and didn't know how to \Nreturn to this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:22:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...after you ran away from \Nthe Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who brought you back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thankful that \NI was living outside of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you are talking about was a small favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Nyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always keep an eye on \Nyou three as a mother would!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call it "small \Nfavor", Snake Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get your hands off of me! Mari! Sonia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...look down on me; a former slave?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you - I hate \Nthe Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that you had one more wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you want to go?\N I'll give you a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kuja Pirates hold a banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Luffy is mobbed by curious women,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margaret saves him and takes \Nhim to Granny Nyon's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there, Luffy finds out that \Nhis brother Ace is in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's forced to make a big decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Saving Ace!\N The Next Stop: the Great Prison!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
